README

SUMMARY
-------

The coupler is a package for parallel data transfer between arbitrary physics 
codes. Interfaces are provided for data access to each physics. See doxygen
documentation for more details.


DEPENDENCIES
------------

The coupler depends on the nemesis library as well as the following 
Trilinos packages:

*: Teuchos


CONFIGURE
---------

The coupler uses the TriBITS cmake build system. See doc/build_notes/ for 
configure information as well as a sample script.

BUILD
-----

make - Standard build.

make test - Standard build and unit tests.

make doc - Generate doxygen documentation.
